Dr Govind K Gupta, MBBS from Calcutta National Medical College and Diplomat, American Board of Sexology, is India's most widely acclaimed and experienced sexologist having treated over one lakh patients. Experienced physician in Sexual Problems, Infertility and Sexually Transmitted Diseases.

Dr. Anirban Chakraborty is a leading physician, cardiovascular and diabetes specialist in Kolkata who is trained to an international standard in UK and USA. He practices diabetes, cardiovascular medicine, respiratory medicine and internal medicine in Kolkata. Dr. Chakraborty works as a senior consultant in  R.N Tagore Hospital in Kolkata and Narayana Health Super Specialty Hospital. He also works as a Consultant part-time in the National Health Service in England. You can rest assured that by consulting him you will get the most modern, latest and safest treatment in the world, here in Kolkata.  Dr. Anirban Chakraborty had worked as a substantive consultant in the UK (total for three years) after completing his specialist registrar's training (CCST or CCT). He obtained the prestigious FRCP degree at the age of 37 from the Royal College of Physicians UK. He still maintains the high standard required to work in the UK (he does that for a few weeks every year as a consultant) and keeps himself updated by attending Royal College Conferences in the UK, among others.  He is only a handful of doctors in the whole of India to have achieved the above credentials of having a specialty training from the UK (CCST), the highest degree for physicians in the UK (FRCP) and the experience of working as a substantive consultant in NHS UK. Dr. Chakraborty has extensive experience of over 13 years of working in the UK and USA, where he went with the prestigious Fogarty Scholarship in 2002. Dr. Chakraborty has worked as a substantive consultant in the Dudley Group Of Hospitals, and later as a senior consultant in internal medicine at Queen Elizabeth Hospital Birmingham; one of the largest super specialty hospitals in the world. He promises to provide an honest, competent and world-class medical consultation in Kolkata by following the latest international guidelines and protocols.   Dr. Anirban Chakraborty is still working part-time as a Consultant in NHS UK where he travels regularly. Getting his opinion on your medical problem will give you the peace of mind of getting the latest and safest view of an internationally recognized and trained doctor without the hassle of traveling out of Kolkata.

The doctor has immense experience in this field. Dr. Sandip Rungta at girish park is a leading cardiologist who is visited by a large number of patients suffering from heart conditions. In addition to dealing with conditions like congenital heart defects, coronary artery diseases, heart failures, valvular heart diseases and electrophysiology, the doctor also offers diagnosis and treatment of certain conditions related to some parts of the circulatory system. Some of the common types of heart conditions that the doctor treats include rheumatic heart disease, hypertensive heart disease, ischemic heart disease, cerebrovascular disease and inflammatory heart disease. The doctor has a polite approach towards patients and is known for the personal care and attention offered to every single patient.
